# Capstan Walk — Illustration Prompt

Create a richly detailed, roughly square digital painting sized to sit beside narrative text on desktop or mobile screens. Depict a grounded late-medieval harbor campaign setting with a large ship-hauling capstan, timber bars, heavy line, harbor crew, and practical dockside machinery. Emphasize crisp readability, brighter maritime color accents, and clear spatial separation more than muddy painterly atmosphere.

- Composition: circular capstan yard with the path back toward Rope Crane Pier still obvious.
- Key elements: waiting hauling crew, capstan bars, line under tension-ready slack, and a bench with tally items.
- Character focus: crew who are plainly prepared to work but have not been formally told to begin.
- Navigation hint: keep the return path toward the main pier visible and legible.

